## Accessibility Requirements

### Reduced Motion (CRITICAL)

**Must include in ALL CSS files:**

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *,
  *::before,
  *::after {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

**What This Disables:**

- Entrance animations
- Continuous pulses/shimmers
- Hover transforms
- Background gradients
- ALL decorative motion

**What Stays Enabled:**

- Instant color changes
- Focus indicators (no transition)
- Static shadows
- Layout shifts (but instant)

### Focus States

**Required for keyboard navigation:**

```css
button:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--accent-primary);
  outline-offset: 3px;
}
```

**Applied to:**

- All interactive elements
- Form inputs
- Navigation links
- Cards (when clickable)

### Color Contrast

**Minimum Ratios (WCAG AA):**

- Normal text: 4.5:1
- Large text (≥18px): 3:1
- UI components: 3:1

**Current Compliance:**

- ✅ Text Primary on BG: 15:1
- ✅ Text Secondary on BG: 7:1
- ✅ Accent Blue on Dark: 8:1

