## When NOT to Animate

### ❌ Forbidden Patterns

1. **Continuous motion without purpose**
   - Floating elements
   - Rotating logos
   - Endless bouncing

2. **Animation on every element**
   - Text appearing letter-by-letter
   - Each list item fading in separately
   - Simultaneous transforms everywhere

3. **Heavy animations on scroll**
   - Parallax on mobile
   - Scroll-triggered reveals (use entrance once)

4. **Distracting backgrounds**
   - Video backgrounds
   - Particle systems
   - Complex SVG animations

### ✅ Approved Use Cases

1. **Entrance:** Page/section load (once)
2. **Feedback:** Hover, click, focus (reversible)
3. **Status:** Live, error, loading (semantic)
4. **Progress:** Shimmer on active bars (contextual)

### Decision Matrix

| Scenario | Animate? | Why |
|----------|----------|-----|
| Page loads | ✅ Yes | Perceived performance |
| Card hovers | ✅ Yes | Immediate feedback |
| Live badge | ✅ Yes | Critical status |
| Background | ⚠️ Subtle only | Must be < 15s, low opacity |
| Logo | ❌ No | Distraction |
| Text entry | ❌ No | Usability issue |

