## Contract Rules & Stop Criteria

> **CTO Enforcement:** These are mechanically checkable. Violations = PR rejection.

### Stop Criterion #1: No Glow Outside Status

**Allowed Glow States:**
- `[data-state="live"]` - Live broadcasts (amber pulse)
- `[data-state="recording"]` - Active recordings (amber pulse)
- `[data-state="error"]` - Critical errors (red pulse)

**Forbidden:**
- Card hover glow
- Navigation item glow (use inset bar instead)
- Button glow (use solid shadow)
- Decorative glow

**Enforcement:** Search codebase for `box-shadow.*glow|rgba.*0\.[3-9]` outside status selectors.

### Stop Criterion #2: Continuous Motion = Status Pulse Only

**Allowed:**
```css
@keyframes statusPulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50% { opacity: 0.6; }
}

/* Applied ONLY to: */
.status-chip[data-state="live"] .status-chip__icon,
.status-chip[data-state="recording"] .status-chip__icon,
.status-indicator[data-state="error"]
```

**Forbidden:**
- Background gradient animation
- Progress bar shimmer
- Button ripple effects
- Rotating/floating elements
- Any `animation` with `infinite` outside status pulse

**Enforcement:** Search for `animation.*infinite` - must only appear in status contexts.

### Token Compliance

**Required:**
- All colors from `--bg-*`, `--text-*`, `--accent-*`, `--status-*`
- All typography from `--font-*`, `--text-*`
- All spacing from `--radius-*`

**Forbidden:**
- Hardcoded hex colors (e.g., `#3b82f6` instead of `var(--accent-action)`)
- Magic numbers for font-size (use tokens)
- Inline gradient definitions (use token-based patterns)

**Enforcement:** Lint check for `#[0-9a-f]{3,6}` in CSS files outside token definitions.

