> **Critical:** Continuous motion is FORBIDDEN except status pulse.

### Allowed Motion

**1. Entrance (One-Time):**
```css
@keyframes enterFade {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

duration: 200ms;
easing: ease-out;
once: true;
```

**2. Interactions:**
```css
transition: all 180ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
```

**3. Status Pulse (Infinite):**
```css
@keyframes statusPulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50% { opacity: 0.6; }
}

duration: 2s;
iteration-count: infinite;
/* ONLY for LIVE/REC/ERROR */
```

### Deprecated Motion (v1.0 - REMOVED)

 **Removed:**
- `@keyframes fadeInUp` with translateY
- `@keyframes shimmer` for progress bars
- `@keyframes gradientShift` for backgrounds
- Button ripple effects
- Card entrance animations with transform

### Reduced Motion (Mandatory)

**Must be in ALL CSS files:**
```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *,
  *::before,
  *::after {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

