## Review Checklist

Before submitting changes:

**Contract Compliance:**
- [ ] All colors use tokens (no hardcoded hex)
- [ ] Fonts use `--font-heading|body|mono` (not `--font-main`)
- [ ] Motion respects 2s-max for interactions, infinite only for status
- [ ] Glow appears ONLY on status elements
- [ ] Tabular numbers applied to technical data

**Stop Criteria:**
- [ ] No gradients outside status cards
- [ ] No continuous animations outside status pulse
- [ ] LIVE/REC uses amber (`--accent-live`)
- [ ] ERROR uses red (`--status-error`)

**Accessibility:**
- [ ] Reduced-motion support present
- [ ] Focus states visible (no glow, use outline)
- [ ] Touch targets ≥ 44px

**Performance:**
- [ ] Grain/scanline opacity ≤ 0.04
- [ ] No repaint on scroll
- [ ] Transitions ≤ 220ms

